Xavier Leroy


[English version:]
------------------

An embarassing bug has been discovered in the 0.72 version of Caml Light,
so it is our pleasure to announce the release of Caml Light version 0.73.

This version also corrects the problems reported when Caml Light is
running under Windows 3.1. In addition, the Windows and Macintosh
versions now offer the bignum rational arithmetic package (module num.ml).

This release is available as:

 - sources and diffs for Unix.
 - binaries for RedHat Linux.
 - binaries for MSWindows (NT, 95, 3.1).
 - binaries for Macintosh.

host: ftp.inria.fr (192.93.2.54)
directory: lang/caml-light

url: ftp://ftp.inria.fr/lang/caml-light/

Bug reports should be mailed to caml-light@pauillac.inria.fr.

Damien Doligez
Pierre Weis
Xavier Leroy





